1
00:00:59,000 --> 00:00:59,800
Report!

2
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:04,040
General, the Empress Dowager is missing.

3
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,120
What?

4
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,480
The camp is crude.

5
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:24,320
I cannot bear to see the Empress Dowager suffer.

6
00:01:24,320 --> 00:01:28,039
So I took her to stay with the Helian clan for a few days.

7
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,680
When the Great General returns,

8
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,039
she will be sent back immediately.

9
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:33,720
Helian Jie has abducted the Empress Dowager.

10
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:37,200
Men, assemble the troops and head to the Helian clan immediately.

11
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,000
Wait.

12
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:40,960
Young General, what do you mean?

13
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,280
You guard this place.

14
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,120
Leave this matter to me.

15
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:49,060
Thank you, Young General.

16
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,080
General,

17
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:57,210
are we just going to let this go?

18
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,979
It doesn't matter.

19
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:03,040
The gold vein is the most important thing.

20
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,520
There can be no mistakes.

21
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,680
Otherwise, if the Great General blames us,

22
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,080
I won't be able to bear it.

23
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,440
Besides,

24
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:11,680
we met the Empress Dowager by accident,

25
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,880
and now she's been taken away by Helian Jie.

26
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,940
Even if trouble arises in the future,

27
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,640
it has nothing to do with me.

28
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,560
Understood.

29
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,090
Let's go.

30
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:35,440
Young Master.

31
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,700
Where is Her Ladyship?

32
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:37,650
Where is she now?

33
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,160
Aren't you quite good at predicting things?

34
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,890
Do you still need me to tell you?

35
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,120
Return to Wuse City.

36
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,480
Why are you suddenly in a rush to return to Wuse City?

37
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,640
A'man secretly kidnapped Ji Mingyue.

38
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,400
The Helian Clan has long been oppressed by the imperial court.

39
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,800
Every year on the Empress Dowager's birthday,

40
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:53,120
the court would take the opportunity to demand an additional 50,000 taels of gold as tribute.

41
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,800
The entire Helian Clan has hated her to the bone for a long time.

42
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,600
If she is brought to the Helian Clan now,

43
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,240
not only will she be in danger,

44
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:02,040
but the Helian Clan will also be pushed to the forefront of the storm.

45
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,280
A'man's action

46
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,920
undoubtedly adds fuel to the fire.

47
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:05,720
A'man

48
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,200
is too willful.

49
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,000
Are you going to find her?

50
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:13,880
Of course.

51
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:36,500
Greetings, young master.

52
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,800
Empress Dowager.

53
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,860
Don't look at me like that.

54
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:53,480
I just used a little trick

55
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,640
so you can't use your magic.

56
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,440
Without your magic

57
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,920
and the unique acupoint sealing technique

58
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,920
of our Helian clan,

59
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,840
you

60
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,080
can't undo it.

61
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:17,760
Young Master, they are...

62
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:21,959
The Demon Empress, Ji Mingyue.

63
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,360
What?

64
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,520
Take them inside.

65
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,520
Yes, sir.

66
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,440
Move!

67
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:34,720
Move!

68
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:37,880
Hurry up!

69
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,600
Young Master.

70
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:43,480
The letter you told me to send to General Shen in the capital

71
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,680
has been delivered.

72
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,040
Good.

73
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,520
Shen Lian is coming too.

74
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,440
Then Wuse City

75
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:53,400
will have its liveliest day in history.

76
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,360
Shen Lian is coming.

77
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,280
Does the High Priest know?

78
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,420
My father is in seclusion.

79
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,130
He doesn't need to know.

80
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:11,680
That bitch used my father for years.

81
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,480
It's time for her to pay.

82
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,400
Shen Lian.

83
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:17,000
The Emperor has his eyes on her.

84
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:19,280
I'm afraid she won't be able to leave the city.

85
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,840
You underestimate her.

86
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,600
She is formidable.

87
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,880
She values wealth and power above all.

88
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,720
Tell me,

89
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:32,180
if she hears Baili Jinghong was secretly assassinated by my brother,

90
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,720
that several gold veins are now ownerless,

91
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,240
and that she is desperately needed

92
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,240
to take charge,

93
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,159
could she resist coming?

94
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,120
Give me back my son!

95
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,360
Demon Empress!

96
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,420
Give me back my son!

97
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,720
Demon Empress!

98
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,020
Demon Empress,

99
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,850
you ruined our country!

100
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,740
Give me back my son!

101
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,780
Demon Empress,

102
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,680
go to hell!

103
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,960
Go to hell!

104
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:05,820
Demon Empress,

105
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,960
you ruined our country!

106
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,090
It's all your fault!

107
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,740
Demon Empress!

108
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,080
How dare you harm us!

109
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,440
Why don't you just die?

110
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,300
Demon Empress,

111
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,480
beat her to death!

112
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,810
The corruption of a dynasty

113
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:23,520
always uses women as scapegoats.

114
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,640
A hundred years from now,

115
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,280
will history books also claim

116
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:30,440
that I am the demon empress who ruined the Dayin court?

117
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,760
It's ridiculous. Why?

118
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:37,200
Why does history only blame women for ruining the country,

119
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:40,000
but never records their merits and achievements?

120
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,720
Why are women merely tools to bear shame

121
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,280
and infamous reputations?

122
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:48,540
It is only because, since ancient times,

123
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:51,320
no woman has ever sat on the supreme throne.

124
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:55,800
Therefore, the snobbish masses

125
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:58,040
never speak up for them.

126
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,200
How do you have the nerve to live?

127
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,360
Demon Empress!

128
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,120
You monster!

129
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,320
Die!

130
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:09,090
How do you still have the nerve to live?

131
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,760
Just die, Demon Empress!

132
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:16,690
The eldest young master has returned to the city!

133
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:19,610
The eldest young master has returned to the city!

134
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:23,760
The eldest young master is back!

135
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,560
Eldest young master!

136
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:30,840
Go, bathe Her Grace and change her clothes.

137
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:31,640
Yes.

138
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,100
Your Highness.

139
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:40,760
Please don't blame me for sealing your acupoints again.

140
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:43,040
Your methods are too formidable.

141
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,400
I was forced to do this.

142
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,480
I have no choice but to wrong you.

143
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:50,200
Your Highness, are you satisfied with this one?

144
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,640
Change the pearl hairpin.

145
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,840
This one is too tacky.

146
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,720
Brother won't like it.

147
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,280
Yes.

148
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,800
Then how about this one?

149
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,080
Dressed up like this,

150
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:14,880
Your Highness is truly stunning.

151
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:18,160
Don't worry. I have no interest in you.

152
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,040
Aman is of great importance.

153
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,450
Where exactly is the Empress Dowager?

154
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,000
Don't rush, brother.

155
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,840
Get some rest.

156
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,080
You will see her soon.

157
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,640
There have been many coincidences on this journey.

158
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,570
What is going on?

159
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:56,040
Mother, why are you here?

160
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,680
If I hadn't come,

161
00:08:57,680 --> 00:09:00,200
how would I know you've completely lost your mind?

162
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:03,120
Ji Mingyue is just a stepping stone in our plan.

163
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:05,560
Instead of figuring out how to take over

164
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,880
all of Baili Jinghong's gold veins,

165
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:11,220
you actually fell for her at a time like this.

166
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,520
If Helian Jie hadn't told me,

167
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,360
I wouldn't have believed it.

168
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:17,200
You've only seen her a few times,

169
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,880
and you already like her?

170
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,080
When I was young,

171
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,520
my father doted on me.

172
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,120
He sent the best guards to protect me

173
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:33,440
and the best painters to make me happy.

174
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:37,480
But I just couldn't be happy no matter what.

175
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,760
Mother, do you know why?

176
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,840
Because everyone had a mother,

177
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:45,920
except me.

178
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,040
After Aman was born,

179
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,240
he was sickly.

180
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:59,240
Father cared for him so much

181
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,480
that he liked me less.

182
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,840
I became even more unhappy.

183
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,880
Countless times, I fantasized

184
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:09,680
and wondered:

185
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:12,840
Did my mother

186
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,240
not love me?

187
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,240
Otherwise,

188
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,840
why didn't she come to see me?

189
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,280
Jin.

190
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,040
Later, I found out

191
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,800
that a child took my place

192
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,050
and became Mother's child.

193
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,920
So I sent painters and guards

194
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,050
to secretly record their lives

195
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,280
for me to imagine.

196
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:04,160
Mother treated her so well.

197
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:08,040
In summer, you would push her on the swing

198
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:11,080
and teach her archery yourself.

199
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:13,020
You would even personally

200
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:15,250
make her tremella and lotus seed soup.

201
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,960
To this day,

202
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,680
I haven't even tasted

203
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,880
the lotus seed soup you made.

204
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,920
I was really jealous of her then.

205
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,400
My jealousy turned into hatred.

206
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,960
I couldn't accept it.

207
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:36,560
Why could she take my place

208
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:37,920
and get your love?

209
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,340
But later she entered the palace,

210
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:44,240
eliminated enemies for you,

211
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,530
and was labeled a disaster to the country.

212
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:50,280
She was insulted

213
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:53,890
and became a demon queen everyone wanted to kill.

214
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:01,380
Then I started to feel guilty and blamed myself.

215
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,360
Was it

216
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,480
because of me

217
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,560
that a girl had to bear

218
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:10,960
the responsibilities I should have borne?

219
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,280
Why are you comparing yourself to her?

220
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,480
She's just from the General's manor,

221
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,680
a piece of trash born to a lowly servant.

222
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:21,360
It was I who taught her consistently for ten years,

223
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:23,420
so she could have her current skills.

224
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:25,060
But you're different.

225
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,740
You are extraordinarily gifted.

226
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:29,610
She can't compare to you at all.

227
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,340
You're wrong, Mother.

228
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:33,890
She is not trash.

229
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:38,080
She is the light in my heart.

230
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,640
You are right.

231
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,140
I really haven't seen her many times.

232
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,240
But it feels like

233
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:48,760
I have loved her for a very long time.

234
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,320
Just like

235
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:55,000
from the day I started expecting you to love me,

236
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,040
that long.

237
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:12,720
What is it?

238
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,320
To answer the First Young Master,

239
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,880
I wanted to see if the Empress Dowager

240
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:17,080
needed any water.

241
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:19,960
What did you say?

242
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,200
Empress Dowager?

243
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:22,680
Yes.

244
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,000
You may leave first.

245
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:25,800
Yes.

246
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,240
Mingyue,

247
00:13:58,040 --> 00:13:58,840
I...

248
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:38,320
Is this the truth?

249
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:44,400
So I'm not your child.

250
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:49,320
I'm just a pawn you raised from childhood.

251
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:53,960
A piece of trash born to a lowly maid of the General's Manor.

252
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,640
A stepping stone.

253
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,200
Your child

254
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:07,200
is him.

255
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:18,840
Young General Jiuying of the Northern Frontier.

256
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:22,480
Helian Jin of the Helian Clan.

257
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:36,080
Very well.

258
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,980
Deceiving me over and over again.

259
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,600
You truly are mother and son.

260
00:15:45,280 --> 00:15:46,080
Cut the crap.

261
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,780
Give me the ledger.

262
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,680
Even now,

263
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:55,120
you're still thinking about the ledger.

264
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:56,180
Give me the ledger.

265
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,040
Hurry up.

266
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,960
Mother, we can talk about the ledger later.

267
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,760
Let's first...
